OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMatthew Perry 'found       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpurpose in helping addicts'
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Matthew Perry was "happy and chipper"  
OL,6, when Friends co-creator Marta Kauffman 
OL,7, spoke to him two weeks ago, she says.  
OL,9,FPerry, who played Chandler in the TV   
OL,10,Fsitcom, died on Saturday aged 54.      
OL,12,FKauffman told NBC's Today programme    
OL,13,Ftheir last chat had been "great",      
OL,14,Fadding: "He was in a really good place,
OL,15,Fwhich is why this seems so unfair."    
OL,17,FPerry had battled addictions to alcohol
OL,18,Fand drugs for most of his life, but    
OL,19,FKauffman said: "He wanted to help other
OL,20,Faddicts and it gave him purpose."      
